Chapter 12

The journey to the mountains was long and treacherous, but Kion pressed on, driven by his determination to protect the innocent. When he finally reached the foot of the mountain range, he was met by a group of local animals who had also come to confront the dragon.

Together, Kion and the other animals began to climb the mountain, facing a series of challenges and obstacles along the way. But as they neared the dragon's lair, they knew that their greatest challenge lay ahead.
